  "title": "Invocation for someone you have spoken ill to",
  "source": "Hisn al-Muslim 230",
  "arabic": "قَالَ النَّبِيُّ صلى الله عليه وسلم اللَّهُمَّ فَأَيُّمَا مُؤْمِنٍ سَبَبْتُهُ فَاجْعَلْ ذَلِكَ لَهُ قُرْبَةً إِلَيْكَ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ",
  "meaning": "O Allah, to any believer whom I have insulted, let that be cause to draw him near to You on the Day of Resurrection.",
